&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;sync work indefault task-x&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;count down&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;async work indefault task-y&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Instead I get:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;sync work indefault task-1&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;async work indefault task-1&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;nothing anymore since the runnable is executed in the caller thread&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
